title: The Enemy of My Enemy is My Trend 3/10: Harvard, AR-14, DemExit, COD BattleRoyale

description:
On this edition of the Enemy of My Enemy is My Trend Jack and Miles discussing Harvard kicking kids out of dorms with little notice, Biden argues with a factory worker about guns, people are threatening to leave the Democratic Party if Sanders loses, and Call of Duty has released a stand-alone Battly Royale mode.
